OL,3,CPolice officer admits sent 'sexualised
OL,4,Cmessages' to crime victim
OL,6,FA former South Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Fofficer has pleaded guilty to sending
OL,8,Finappropriate messages to a vulnerable
OL,9,Fvictim of crime.
OL,11,FStuart Trentham, 40, who was based in
OL,12,FDoncaster, admitted sending
OL,13,Fincreasingly flirtatious and
OL,14,Fsexualised messages to a victim when
OL,15,Fhe was investigating her case.
OL,17,FThe victim reported the messages in
OL,18,FAugust 2022 after she noticed a shift
OL,19,Fin the tone of the conversation, which
OL,20,Fhad initially been about her case.
