OL,3,CPolice officer admits sent 'sexualised
OL,4,Cmessages' to crime victim
OL,6,FOfficers in the force's Professional
OL,7,FStandards Department launched an
OL,8,Fimmediate investigation and arrested
OL,9,FTrentham on 23 August 2022.
OL,11,FHe was suspended from duties on the
OL,12,Fsame day.
OL,14,FIn a police interview, Trentham answer
OL,15,F'no comment' to all questions but
OL,16,Finvestigators were able to charge him
OL,17,Fafter finding crucial evidence of
OL,18,Fmessages sent from his devices between
OL,19,FJuly and August 2022.
