OL,3,CPolice officer admits sent 'sexualised
OL,4,Cmessages' to crime victim
OL,6,FHe resigned from the force on 2
OL,7,FDecember, 2023.
OL,9,FTrentham pleaded guilty to one count
OL,10,Fof wilful misconduct and wilfully
OL,11,Fneglecting to perform his duty as a
OL,12,Fholder of a public office at Sheffield
OL,13,FCrown Court on Wednesday 9 October.
OL,15,FThe hearing found that the allegations
OL,16,Fconstituted gross misconduct and that
OL,17,FTrentham would have been dismissed
OL,18,Ffrom the force without notice, had he
OL,19,Fnot already resigned.
